doctor.name: Dr. Bijoy Chandra Das
doctor.info: Dr. Bijoy Chandra Das is a Dentist in Narayanganj. His qualification is BDS, BCS (Health), FICD, PGT (OMS). He is a Consultant, Dental at 300 Bed Hospital, Narayanganj. He regularly provides treatment to his patients at Comfort Dental Care. Practicing hour of Dr. Bijoy Chandra Das at Comfort Dental Care is 6pm to 10pm (Closed: Friday).
